1. *Planirao* je da ode na odmor ove godine. (He planned to go on vacation this year.)
2. On je *planirao* da putuje u inostranstvo. (He planned to travel abroad.)
3. *Planirala* je da napravi pauzu u studiranju. (She planned to take a break from studying.)
4. *Planirali* smo da posetimo Italiju. (We planned to visit Italy.)
5. *Planirano* je bilo da se stvari odlože za sledeću nedelju. (It was planned to postpone things for the next week.)
6. *Planiraju* da izgrade novu kuću. (They are planning to build a new house.)